<table><tr><td>Wilkins E, Nelson M, Agarwal K, Awoyemi D, Barnes E, Bhagani S, Brook G, Brown A, Castelino S, Cooke G, Fisher M, Geretti AM, James R, Kulasegaram R, Leen C, Mutimer D, Orkin C, Page E, Palfreeman A, Papineni P, Rodger A, Tong CY. British HIV Association guidelines for the management of hepatitis viruses in adults infected with HIV 2013. HIV Med. 2013 Nov;14(Suppl 4):1-71. [413 references] <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180712184631/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=Retrieve&amp;db=pubmed&amp;dopt=Abstract&amp;list_uids=24581304" target="_blank">PubMed</a> <img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712184631im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712184631/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=47758&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fwww.bhiva.org%252fdocuments%252fGuidelines%252fHepatitis%252f2013%252fHepatitisGuidelines2013.pdf">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712184631im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
