                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: Brook G, Main J, Nelson M et al. for the BHIVA Viral Hepatitis Working Group. British HIV Association guidelines for the management of coinfection with HIV-1 and hepatitis B or C virus 2010. HIV Med 2010;11:1&ndash;30.</p></div></p>
